                                                <h1 style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;">VISIT US</h1>
                                                <p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">A modern take on the neighborhood eateries found throughout Italy, Mora blends a stylish and tailored aesthetic with relaxed and communal vibes in an expansive dining room, bustling bar and street-side patio. On the menu, chef Scott Conant’s contemporary approach to Italian cooking reimagines time-honored classics such as rich polenta with porcini sugo, and makes bold new impressions with innovative fare such as black campanelle pasta with clams, fresno chilis and bottarga breadcrumbs. Gather your friends for a convivial dining experience at Mora Italian… your table is waiting!&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
